      • getMessageStructureForEvent

        public String getMessageStructureForEvent(String eventName,
                                          ca.uhn.hl7v2.Version version)
                                   throws ca.uhn.hl7v2.HL7Exception
        Looks up its own event map. If no structure was found, the call is delegated to the default ModelClassFactory. If nothing can be found, the eventName is returned as structure. Fixes bug #213 in HAPI 2.2
        Specified by:
